Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:03.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the battle part of day \Nfour of the Grand Magic Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:06.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Due to the disqualification of Raven Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:10.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fairy Tail's A and B teams have merged \Nand are now in a tag team battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Their opponents are Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:16.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a dream showdown between \Nfour Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who will win, Fairy or Tiger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:53.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting and Rogue...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Twin Dragons of Fiore's \Nstrongest guild are on the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He really is strong... But I'd \Nbe disappointed otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:04.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:09.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you two really defeat \Ndragons with power like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:14.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I killed a dragon with this very hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it your parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's got nothin' to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:23.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,From now, I'm gonna show you \Nthe power that killed a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,White Drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shadow Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:43.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting and Rogue, the Twin \NDragons of Sabertooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:47.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dragon Slayers, like Natsu and Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But their magic is still an unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:53.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:56.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I think they're done testing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:00.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,From here on in, they're going to get \Nserious, so let's really cheer them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's over, garbage guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:10.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Alright, the silent face-off continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:13.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but the entire arena \Nis filled with tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Which side will make the first move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sabertooth's Sting makes his move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fairy Tail's Natsu held it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:30.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Receive Holy White Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:44.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! It looks like Fairy Tail's Gajeel \Nis at the mercy of Rogue's Shadow Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't get ahold of shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Squabbling in the middle of a match?! \NYou guys sure have confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Their power has suddenly increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that a kind of Dragon Slayer Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Take care of business, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:17.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! You've gotten \Nfaster for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:21.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, Natsu-san! \NYou call that defense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What on Earthland...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a magic amplification technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On top of that, their combination \Nskills are seamless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This isn't as thrilling as I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:41.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Compared to those two, it seems Fairy \NTail's duo aren't in sync with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:46.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! You're in your assured victory pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fro thinks so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Four Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:57.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The tone of the crowd's cheering has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu-san and Gajeel-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...may be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:15.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's only just begun. There's \Nno need to be so anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:20.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I admired you for the longest time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:25.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And then I set my sights on surpassing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now is that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That attack just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's something different about \Nit compared to previous attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And what the hell is that?! It \Nlooks like a Magic Circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,C-Can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Claw of the White \NDragon is a holy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:55.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A body that's marked by its \Nstigmata loses its freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And with this, I'll surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The dragon that becomes \Nshadow hides its form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It always takes down its prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It always takes down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the way, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He caught him! Even though before, \Nhe wasn't even able to land a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:30.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course! After fighting for a \Nwhile, Gajeel gets used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu can do the same thing with ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:35.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get 'im, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How can you move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:49.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You burned off the stigmata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not too shabby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But you've got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:59.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He burned it off... That \Nguy knows no bounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Only the Salamander could do \Nthat..." I guess I should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:05.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't get too stuck on yourselves, brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And don't make light of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like that! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was great, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:19.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I can't breathe... Calm down, Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:25.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! The course of the \Nbattle has just shifted again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:29.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You guys really are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We have to give this our all and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:41.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Fist of the White Dragon even \Nreduces flames to smithereens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:45.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is that magic?! The \Npressure is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't like this... I think it might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:51.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-So bright! Yajima-san, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:56.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun is concentrating his \Nmagic into a single point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here I go, Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dragon Slayer Arcana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:30.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He stopped that tremendous \Nattack with one hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have no memory of that \Nskill ever being blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:47.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now it makes sense why he would \Nstorm into our inn on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:52.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I could have seen \Nif I hadn't stopped him then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yajima-san, what do you make of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rogue...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:14.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So three months of training and Second Origin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,made these two this strong, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They belong to totally different ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even I can pick up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The way they're cheering \Nhas changed again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I just can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu and Gajeel will win, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:52.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who could have foreseen this development?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:57.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The Twin Dragons of Sabertooth, \Nhelpless before Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will the match end like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like hell it'll end...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:10.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew this wasn't gonna be \Nan easy wall to get over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know, Lector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We made a promise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For Lector's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:58.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tremble at the true power \Nof the Third Generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:02.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible! They can activate \Nit with their own will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dragon Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:09.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu kinda looked like that \Nat the Tower of Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:16.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...he gained the power \Nthen by eating Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:22.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And that time with Zero too, he unleashed \Nthat power by eating all of my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:27.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But they're able to release the \Npower of the Dragon by willing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:34.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the Third Generation \Nof Dragon Slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rogue, hang back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can take both of them on by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:03.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,U-Until just a minute ago, \NSabertooth was being dominated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably, he's challenged both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how much confidence he has, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun and Rogue-kun have Dragon Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way they can lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was worried for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fro forgot about Dragon Force, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:26.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen it yet, but \Nis it really all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At this rate, the \Nodds are against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's gotten quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No. It begins here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shall I check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Natsu and Gajeel will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're lookin' down on us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's different...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Totally different from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:30.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Breath of the White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We can feel the magic at this distance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's because it's a battle \Nbetween Dragon Slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The cost is going to be heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear! What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The floor of the arena is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...crumbling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was one fierce breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What incredible force...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:12.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this the power of the Third \NGeneration Dragon Slayers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems the battlefield is \Nmoving underneath the arena,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but the match will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:26.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please enjoy it on Lacrima-Vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:38.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sword Horn of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Roar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:57.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The light of the White Dragon \Npurifies all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:07.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy attribute magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu can't guard against him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What happened to that confident \Nmood from just before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting-kun really is strong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:53.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fro thinks so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:57.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lector... I made you a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...so I'm definitely gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:13.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Were you bullied again, Lector?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all... nobody believes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told them you beat a dragon, Sting-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Never mind jerks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't! They were saying bad \Nthings about you, Sting-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:44.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate it when people say \Nbad things about my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:53.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I'll prove you're not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:17:01.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There may not be any more dragons, but there \Nis somebody called "Salamander", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:06.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One day, I'll beat him, \Nright in front of everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you watching this, Lector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm watching, Sting-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's become quiet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:41.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Could those tremors from before mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's alright. I mean, it's {\i1}those two{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu... Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Times change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:02.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The span of seven years has allowed us \Nto develop into true Dragon Slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:05.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The time of the old generation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:13.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! They're not even twitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:16.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's been a breathless seesaw battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:20.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but has Fairy Tail finally run out of steam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're stronger than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even Natsu and Gajeel can't beat them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn, this sticks in my craw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:37.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu-nii! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But you really were strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:45.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu-san... Gajeel-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are both of them down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Natsu! Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can hear our voices, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The guild's thoughts are one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're one with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:08.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Sorry I took Gajeel-san down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But, y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...I kept my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't be too hasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucy-san! It feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:34.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's them, alright. No matter how many \Ntimes they fall, they always get up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that should \Nbe called tough or stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Awesome! I knew they could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:43.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Levy! Our voices reached 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'd be in a bind if they weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Incredibly, they're alive and kicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:59.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I saw through all of your habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a bad dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fro thinks so, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:15.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your attack timing... Your \Nposture when you defend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even the rhythm of your breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! I'm using Dragon Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:27.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it packs a wallop! \NMy body aches all over, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't get rattled, Sting. He's bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bluffin', you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You really think the Salamander can pull \Noff a trick that requires usin' his brain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:42.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For example, when you attack, \Nyour pivot foot is facing 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's 11:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:50.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I could let you slide with \N10:30, but not 11:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:53.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I say it's 11:00! 23:00 is fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's going around 360 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:03.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are those two fools doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:07.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They've got energy to spare. And that means \Nthey've still got fight left in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Arguing at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeesh, they make me wanna crawl in a hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:18.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be like that. You \Nand Natsu are two of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When you look at me objectively, \Nthat's what you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Clam it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:41.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've totally gotta pay you \Nback for lookin' down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can take both of you on by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, attack me at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:55.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy! Now Natsu Dragneel of Fairy Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:58.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is challenging the two of them to a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:02.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're fired up, ain'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:36.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:40.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I swear, later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu, I trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:23:59.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me. Keep believin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'd never betray me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:03.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought this was about \Nthe match... Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:06.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu, you'd never do anything \Nto make me sad, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:08.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let anybody make you sad, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen... Somebody ate my fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time: Natsu vs. the Twin Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.19,0:24:18.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Happy... You gotta believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:19.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:22.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't know it was yours, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.75,0:24:24.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsu!
